<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Job Expired â€“ My Car Quote</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .box {
      max-width: 720px;
      width: 100%;
      margin: auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 50px 40px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 26px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .btn-group {
      margin-top: 25px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 8px;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background: #007bff;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 16px;
      min-width: 160px;
    }

    .btn-exit {
      background: #6c757d;
    }

    .small {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .box {
        padding: 30px 20px;
        border-radius: 0;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 17px;
      }

      .btn {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        margin: 10px 0;
        font-size: 18px;
        padding: 14px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div style="text-align:center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <img src="<%= logoUrl || 'http://localhost:3000/img/logo-true.svg' %>" alt="My Car Quote Logo" style="max-width: 150px;">
  </div>

  <div class="box">
    <h2>Hello<%= customerName ? ' ' + customerName : '' %>,</h2>
    <p>Unfortunately, your job request <strong>#<%= job.id %></strong> did not receive any quotes within 48 hours and has now been removed from our system.</p>
    <p>If you'd like to try again, you're welcome to submit a new request at any time.</p>

    <div class="btn-group">
      <a class="btn" href="<%= newRequestUrl %>">Submit New Request</a>
      <a class="btn btn-exit" href="<%= homeUrl %>">Exit</a>
    </div>

    <p class="small">Thank you for using My Car Quote.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>